  <!-- EN: ADS -->
  <PPCADS.label>主动驱敌系统</PPCADS.label>
  <!-- EN: The RA-22 Active Denial System (ADS) is a non-lethal, directed-energy weapon designed for area denial and crowd control. It heats the skin of targeted human subjects causing them to break rank and flee. Does not require line of sight. Requires a manned SACS. -->
  <PPCADS.description>RA-22主动驱敌系统是一种非致命的定向能量武器，它发射的毫米波能让目标皮肤水份沸腾，产生无法忍受的痛苦，使敌人落荒而逃。需要能量武器控制台操纵。</PPCADS.description>
  <!-- EN: AOE +10 -->
  <PPCADS.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.0>AOE +10</PPCADS.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.0>
  
  <!-- EN: HEL -->
  <PPCHEL.label>激光点防御</PPCHEL.label>
  <!-- EN: The RA-702 High Energy Laser (HEL) destroys enemy airborne projectiles such as mortar shells. When a mortar is fired the system will check if the shell will pass through the range of a HEL, and attempt to track the target and fire once it is in range. -->
  <PPCHEL.description>RA-702激光点防御可摧毁敌人的空中投射物，如迫击炮弹。当迫击炮发射时，系统将检测炮弹是否会进入激光点防御的射程，如果进入射程的时间足够长，那么激光点防御将跟踪目标并在目标进入射程内后发射。需要配合能量武器控制台，无人操作时也能照常运行。</PPCHEL.description>
  <!-- EN: Shootdown time -50% -->
  <PPCHEL.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.0>击落耗时 -50%</PPCHEL.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.0>
  <!-- EN: Power +50% -->
  <PPCHEL.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.1>威力 +50%</PPCHEL.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.1>
  
  <!-- EN: Marauder -->
  <PPCMarauder.label>“掠夺者”磁轨炮</PPCMarauder.label>
  <!-- EN: The RA-3b Marauder is a multi-barrel coaxial plasma railgun platform, large electromagnetic pulses fire a burst of accelerated plasma toroids to extreme velocities causing explosive radiation emitting impacts. Requires a manned SACS. -->
  <PPCMarauder.description>RA-3b“掠夺者”磁轨炮是一种多管同轴的等离子轨道炮平台，使用高能电磁脉冲发射一连串高速等离子回旋体，拥有极快的速度。需要有人操作能量武器控制台时才能运行，可选择手动瞄准。</PPCMarauder.description>
  <!-- EN: Burst +10 shots -->
  <PPCMarauder.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.0>连射 +10</PPCMarauder.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.0>
  
  <!-- EN: Obelisk -->
  <PPCObelisk.label>光明石碑</PPCObelisk.label>
  <!-- EN: The RA-2152-X Obelisk is a directed energy weapon that uses a focused solid state laser to vaporize targets. 100% accurate with long range and devastating power. Automatic targeting and firing. Manned SACS required for manual targeting -->
  <PPCObelisk.description>RA-2152-X光明石碑是一种定向能量武器，使用聚能激光灼烧乃至蒸发目标的。精度100%，射程远、威力强，但是耗能高、冷却时间长，可自动瞄准和开火。可配合能量武器控制台手动瞄准，能量武器控制台无人操作时也能照常运行。</PPCObelisk.description>
  <!-- EN: Damage +15% -->
  <PPCObelisk.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.0>伤害 +15%</PPCObelisk.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.0>
  <!-- EN: Pulse Size +15% -->
  <PPCObelisk.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.1>脉冲强度 +15%</PPCObelisk.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.1>
  
  <!-- EN: Punisher -->
  <PPCRailgun.label>“惩戒者”磁轨炮</PPCRailgun.label>
  <!-- EN: The RA-1802D Punisher is a 25 round magazine fed railgun platform which uses large electromagnetic pulses to launch sabot projectiles to extreme velocities and ranges. Requires line of sight. Fire mission does not require line of sight. Manned SACS required for manual targeting. Requires a manned SACS. -->
  <PPCRailgun.description>RA-1802D“惩戒者”磁轨炮是一中拥有25发弹匣的轨道炮平台，使用高能电磁脉冲发射炮弹，拥有极快的速度和极大范围的火力覆盖。需要有人操作能量武器控制台时才能运行，可选择手动瞄准。</PPCRailgun.description>
  <!-- EN: Range +10 Tiles -->
  <PPCRailgun.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.0>火力覆盖 +10 地图格</PPCRailgun.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.0>
  <!-- EN: Pulse Size +15% -->
  <PPCRailgun.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.1>脉冲强度 +15%</PPCRailgun.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.1>
  
  <!-- EN: Tesla Coil -->
  <PPCTeslaCoil.label>磁暴线圈</PPCTeslaCoil.label>
  <!-- EN: The RA-42T Tesla Coil delivers a huge electrical arc discharge to its targets resulting in severe burns or death. 100% accurate, medium range, sets targets on fire. Automatic targeting and firing. Manned SACS required for manual targeting. -->
  <PPCTeslaCoil.description>RA-42T磁暴线圈可瞬间向范围内的任一目标释放强大的电弧，导致严重烧伤或死亡，精度100%，中等范围，可设定攻击目标。配合警戒雷达可自动瞄准和开火。可配合能量武器控制台手动瞄准，能量武器控制台无人操作时也能照常运行。</PPCTeslaCoil.description>
  <!-- EN: Damage +15% -->
  <PPCTeslaCoil.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.0>伤害 +15%</PPCTeslaCoil.comps.CompUpgradable.upgrades.0.stats.0>
  <!-- EN: Range +10 -->
